Install postgresql 7.4
Configure postgresql 7.4
Edit /var/lib/pgsql/postgresql.conf
	Set: #tcpip_socket = false
	To:  tcpip_socket = true
Edit  /var/lib/pgsql/pg_hba.conf
	Set: #host    all         all         127.0.0.1         255.255.255.255   trust
	To:  host    all         all         127.0.0.1         255.255.255.255   trust
Start postgresql 7.4